hopobject.body: How many days will it take for the cheque to clear? buypharmacy.tk Goody, 84, now living in Spain, says he first heard about the robbery plan from crooked solicitors' clerk Brian Field. "I had just been acquitted of a robbery at the Old Bailey and Brian called me into his office. There was no mention of a train â just that there was a large sum of money in transit and a large, well-organised gang would easily be able to liberate it. Brian wanted to know if I was interested."
